                evt.SimpleMessage("Very good…or at least, as good as can be expected. You managed to bring three partners into the alliance--the minimum number my advisors told me would be sufficient to fulfill the \"…Jadame, must stand together…\" part of the prophecy. A pity it could not be more, but events of the cataclysm are clearly coming to a head. It is time to move onward.You must travel to Ravenshore and meet with the alliance council gathered there. With them, decide what must be the next step we take in meeting the elemental crisis.")
