        evt.SimpleMessage("Balthazar Lair has many levels. There are other chambers as high as this one., so there may be others who have survived.I have thought long on this. Though many of the tunnels are flooded, it may be possible to drain them using the doors and air vents as valves. In fact, the whole lair could be drained through the lower level escape tunnel. Help my herd! You would have our eternal gratitude.")
