    evt.SimpleMessage("You seek promotion for the clerics of our faith who travel with you.?\nI can promote you, but I do not place much trust or faith in strangers these days.\nIf you were to do something for me, such as finding the lost Prophecies of the Sun, and returning them to me, then I would be agreeable to promoting you.")
