            evt.SimpleMessage("I can turn a simple Rogue into a fearsome killer, but only if he has the right kind of temperament for the job.\nThe time is coming when you must choose to walk in the light, or in the dark.\nIf you prefer the shadow, come to me and I will complete your training.")
