        evt.SimpleMessage("Ah, fellow Crusaders!\nI know thee thirsts for another task with which to hone thy Crusading skills, but first thee must pass a far more serious test.\nThee must agree to follow the Path of Light before I can help thee further.\nYou will know when you have made this choice.\nReturn to me then.")
    end
end)

