    evt.SetNPCGreeting(384, 182) -- Ebednezer Sower greeting: Bounty Hunters. [Ebednezer smiles slowly and evilly] Now THERE'S a job! Yes sir. Get things done righteo quick, I'll venture. Heh.
end)

