    evt.SimpleMessage("Our allies in Tatalia have been complaining for some time of a mysterious presence.\nThere have been numerous deaths and disappearances for the last few months, and they've asked us if we knew anything about it.\nI think I do.\nI suspect a vampire is preying on Tatalia.\nI don't have time to pursue the question myself, but to keep our allies happy, I'm asking you to please look into it.\nIt's possible the monster's presence has deeper implications than just bad luck for Tatalia.")
    SetQBit(QBit(618)) -- Investigate the Wine Cellar in Tatalia and return to Crag Hack in Castle Lambent in Celeste.
    evt.SetNPCTopic(420, 0, 902) -- Crag Hack topic 0: Vampires
end)
