    evt.SimpleMessage("[Sir Caneghem looks at the jars curiously, as though observing a poisonous snake behind glass] So these are soul jars.\nI expected something more…impressive, I suppose.\nGood job!\n[he takes the case of jars] I will make sure these jars are never seen again.")
